title: Watch: Kid Tells Cop “Suck my f***in' d**k, pu**y!” After Told To Leave McDonalds
description:
Eight “kids” were arrested after they refused to leave a McDonald’s in Massachusetts, according to Fall River Police. They then responded by assaulting officers, WFTX-TV reported.

Officers responded to a report Wednesday afternoon of a group of juveniles causing a disturbance at a nearby CVS. Shortly after, officers learned the delinquents in question had dispersed into a nearby McDonalds.

title: Watch: Wedding party turns chaotic when woman gets knocked out grabbing for a cop's gun, now she's facing multiple felonies
description:
I believe it was Kierkegaard, or maybe it was Mark Davis, who said "Never go to the second place." Nothing good ever happens when you go to the second place, as a group of (assumedly) unsober people learned trying to get into a bar in Rhode Island after a wedding. The bouncer said no. One of the dudes was a dick about it. The cops got called. The women got involved. And one of them wound up unconscious.
